<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="15Jul1928"><font color="red">15 July 1928</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): t13 having at last appeared  we left Paris and are going on today to Austria &hellip; Have you seen WL&apos;s book <i>Childermass</i>? If so, please read carefully pp 90-100 and 170-180. </div>
